# test.cd.pkgdown.gh

<!-- badges: start -->
[![R-CMD-check](https://github.com/ALanguillaume/test.cd.pkgdown.gh/actions/workflows/R-CMD-check.yaml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/ALanguillaume/test.cd.pkgdown.gh/actions/workflows/R-CMD-check.yaml)
<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of test.cd.pkgdown.gh is to test continous deployment of a pkgdown instance via github actions.

## Installation

You can install the development version of test.cd.pkgdown.gh from [GitHub](https://github.com/) with:

``` r
# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("ALanguillaume/test.cd.pkgdown.gh")
```
